'''Sophra''' was the aunt of [[Cray Mingla]] and the sister or sister-in-law of her mother [[Margolis Mingla]]. She constantly criticized Margolis afraid she would show [[Force-sensitive/Legends|sensitivity]] to [[The Force/Legends|The Force]].

{{Char-stub}}

==Behind the scenes==
Sophra is alternately described as Cray's aunt and great-aunt.

